  <!-- VENUES -->
  <section class="home-section" id="venues">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Venues & Fieldhouses</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="d6-venues">

      <div class="d6-venue-card d6-venue-primary">
        <div class="d6-venue-header">
          <h3>District 6 Stadium</h3>
          <span class="tag">Primary Venue</span>
        </div>
        <p class="d6-venue-address">100 71st Avenue, Greeley, CO 80634</p>
        <p>Adjacent to Northridge HS &mdash; the shared home for all three comprehensive high schools.</p>
        <div class="d6-venue-specs">
          <div><strong>Capacity:</strong> ~5,000</div>
          <div><strong>Acreage:</strong> 9+ acres</div>
          <div><strong>Track:</strong> 8-lane</div>
          <div><strong>Fields:</strong> Football + Soccer (natural grass)</div>
        </div>
        <div class="d6-venue-features">
          <span>Announcer's Booth</span>
          <span>TV & Audio Facilities</span>
          <span>Concessions</span>
          <span>Locker Rooms</span>
          <span>Field Events Areas</span>
        </div>
        <p class="d6-venue-note"><strong>Broadcast-ready:</strong> Built with TV facilities, audio booths, and press infrastructure. This is the #1 hardware install target.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="d6-venue-card">
        <div class="d6-venue-header">
          <h3>Greeley Central &mdash; Baggot Gymnasium</h3>
          <span class="tag">Basketball / Volleyball</span>
        </div>
        <p class="d6-venue-address">1515 14th Avenue, Greeley, CO 80631</p>
        <p>On-campus gym inside "The Castle" (1927 Gothic Revival). Additional gym built 1957 at 14th Ave & 16th St.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="d6-venue-card">
        <div class="d6-venue-header">
          <h3>Greeley West &mdash; New Fieldhouse</h3>
          <span class="tag">Basketball / Volleyball</span>
        </div>
        <p class="d6-venue-address">2401 35th Avenue, Greeley, CO 80634</p>
        <p>Brand new 280,000 sq. ft. facility from the 2019 bond. 650-seat auditorium, on-campus gym.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="d6-venue-card">
        <div class="d6-venue-header">
          <h3>Northridge &mdash; On-Campus Gym</h3>
          <span class="tag">Basketball / Volleyball / Wrestling</span>
        </div>
        <p class="d6-venue-address">100 N 71st Avenue, Greeley, CO 80634</p>
        <p>Direct access to District 6 Stadium. On-campus gymnasium for basketball, volleyball, wrestling.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="d6-venue-card">
        <div class="d6-venue-header">
          <h3>Greeley Recreation Center Pool</h3>
          <span class="tag">Swimming (Shared Municipal)</span>
        </div>
        <p class="d6-venue-address">Greeley Recreation Center, Greeley, CO</p>
        <p>8-lane, 25-yard competition pool &mdash; the only competition pool in Greeley. Used by all D6 swim teams.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PARTNERSHIP CONTACT -->
  <section class="home-section home-section-dark" id="partnership">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Partnership & Contact</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="d6-contact">
      <div class="d6-contact-grid">
        <div class="d6-contact-card">
          <h4>District 6 Administration</h4>
          <p>1025 9th Avenue, Greeley, CO 80631</p>
          <p>(970) 348-6000</p>
        </div>
        <div class="d6-contact-card">
          <h4>Director of Athletics & Activities</h4>
          <p>Sean Scribbick</p>
          <p>(970) 348-6302</p>
        </div>
        <div class="d6-contact-card">
          <h4>District Facilities Office</h4>
          <p>2204 5th Avenue, Greeley, CO</p>
          <p>(970) 348-6400</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="d6-cta-box">
        <h3>Want to be a Parent Delegate?</h3>
        <p>If you're a parent who's already in the stands every Friday night, you can help broadcast the game to families across Greeley. We provide the gear and training — you bring the energy.</p>
        <a href="/auth/register" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Sign Up to Volunteer</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- EXISTING STREAMING NOTE -->
  <section class="home-section" id="existing">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Current Landscape</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="d6-mission">
      <p>District 6 currently has 116+ live events available through the <strong>NFHS Network</strong> (subscription-based). GreeAlityTV aims to complement this with <strong>free, community-driven coverage</strong> — parent delegates in the stands, neighborhood watch parties, and highlight reels that belong to Greeley.</p>
      <p><strong>Conference Affiliations:</strong> Greeley Central and Greeley West compete in the <strong>Northern Colorado Athletic Conference</strong>. Northridge competes in the <strong>Longs Peak League</strong>. All three are CHSAA members with full varsity athletic programs.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>

